        {
            "review_id": "226158514",
            "steam_id": "76561198397441491",
            "playtime_minutes": 240,
            "voted_up": true,
            "votes_up": 0,
            "weighted_score": 0.5,
            "steam_purchase": true,
            "review_text": "Good game, especially with friends as you ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥♥ each other or ragebait them for easy laughs.\n\nOnly real nitpicks are I do hope they swap out the AI voices for actual voice lines, even if amateurish real voices will sound so much nicer.\nAnd the game should not be taking 17 gigabytes of space. I play on a laptop because of money constraints so I dont have too much space to spare, and a game as simple as this which you will realistically open only once every few weeks or month to play it with the gang shouldn't take so much space."
        },
        {
